'''"By the Banks of the Warm, Pink Z'gag"''' was a song played by the members of the [[K'zagg Colony]] at the [[Ruurian/Legends|Ruurian]] cocoon-weaving time, during their annual cycle when the [[Larva/Legends|larvae]] gather to grow chrysalis. Simultaneously, last years pupae are emerging from their cocoons as chroma-wings. It is a soft, sad melody played to comfort the individuals in need.<ref name="Lost Legacy">[[Han Solo and the Lost Legacy]]</ref>

The tune was sung by [[S. V. Skynx/Legends|Skynx]], on his [[mission to Dellalt]], to the members of the party while trapped in the hold of the [[Survivors (Dellalt)|Survivors]].<ref name="Lost Legacy" />

